h2. Structure

APP_PATH
  boot.php
  app/
  config/
  log/
  tmp/
  script/
  vendor/medick (MEDICK_PATH)
  vendor/plugins

h2. Medick Initialization

  index.php 
  | boot.php
  |   Medick.prepare_application()
  |     error_handler
  |     load_frameworks
  |       context
  |       logger
  |       plugins
  |       action_controller
  | $d= new Dispatcher (IConfigurator)
  |   setup_logger
  |   load_plugins
  |
  | $d->dispatch()
  |   route_recognision

